# BDD Scenario Generation Skill

## Goal
Convert a requirement into structured behavior scenarios.

## Steps

1. Analyze requirement
2. Identify actors (user/system)
3. Extract behaviors and outcomes
4. Write scenarios in Given / When / Then format
5. Ensure each scenario describes observable behavior only

## Rules
- Do not include implementation details
- Focus on user/system behavior
- One scenario per behavior

## Output
- List of BDD scenarios ready for test design